After first two chapters you will have your own blog working and you'll be ready to publish awesome posts. Though the features are pretty much limited after there two chapters. To make it nicer for your users, you may read also the following chapters and keep improving your app.

You can find the [full application on GitHub |https://github.com/nette/quickstart]. The blog there is little bit more extended comparing to what this tutorial covers, so be ready to learn.

This QuickStart was written for Nette Framework 2.0.10 and PHP 5.3 or newer. Check out your version.

